        <Parent_String>tripods (stands) [300164679], stands by form: base form [300039777], stands by form [300165783], stands (support objects) [300039767], support furniture [300039337], furniture by form or function [300048628], furniture [300037680], furnishings by form or function [300037342], furnishings (works) [300037336], Furnishings (hierarchy name) [300037335], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
